</li><li class="c-issue-toc__article c-issue-toc__article--no-translation" data-aricle-no="01">
	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="413"><a href="/pl/archiwum/2018/20-odmuzealnienie/wojna-wojnie-ernsta-friedricha-jako-montaz">“But all this ‘heroism’ is a lie. Horror is the reality” – “War Against War!” by Ernst Friedrich as a Montage</a></h4>
	<h5 class="c-issue-toc__article-authors"><!--Authors:--><a href="/en/bio?id=412">Marta Maliszewska</a></h5>
	
				<a class="c-issue-toc__article-collapse-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseDoi413" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSummary413" data-lexicon-show="show" data-lexicon-hide="hide">
					citation
